sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationInfo (Iteration, IterationState)

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PppoeSummary_IterationInfo (Iteration, IterationState)
DELETE FROM PppoeSummary_IterationInfo
SELECT * FROM Pppoe_IterationInfo

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationState, Location, EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, SuccSetupRate)

SELECT Iteration, IterationState, Location, EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, SuccSetupRate FROM Pppoe_SessionRateResults WHERE Iteration = (SELECT Iteration FROM PppoeSummary_IterationInfo)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_PortSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, PortName TEXT, Location, ExpectedSessions INTEGER, ConnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, DisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, FailedConnectCount INTEGER, FailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, ConfigConnectRate REAL, SuccSetupRate REAL, MinSetupTime REAL, MaxSetupTime REAL, AvgSetupTime REAL, AvgSuccessTransactionCount INTEGER)

SELECT PR.PortName, Port.Location, PR.Sessions AS ExpectedSessions, PR.ConnectedSuccessCount, PR.DisconnectedSuccessCount, PR.FailedConnectCount, PR.FailedDisconnectCount, PC.ConnectRate AS ConfigConnectRate, SR.SuccSetupRate, SR.MinSetupTime, SR.MaxSetupTime, SR.AvgSetupTime, PR.AvgSuccessTransactionCount FROM PppoxPortConfig AS PC, PppoePortResults AS PR, Port AS Port, Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults AS SR WHERE PC.Handle == PR.ParentHnd AND PC.EmulationType == 'CLIENT' AND Port.Handle == PC.ParentHnd AND SR.Location = Port.Location

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, TotalExpectedSessions INTEGER, TotalSuccessConnectCount INTEGER, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, TotalFailedConnectCount INTEGER, TotalFailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, TotalConfigConnectRate REAL, TotalSuccSetupRate REAL)

SELECT SUM(PR.Sessions) AS TotalExpectedSessions, SUM(PR.ConnectedSuccessCount) AS TotalSuccessConnectCount, SUM(PR.DisconnectedSuccessCount) AS TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount, SUM(PR.FailedConnectCount) AS TotalFailedConnectCount, SUM(PR.FailedDisconnectCount) AS TotalFailedDisconnectCount, SUM(PC.ConnectRate) AS TotalConfigConnectRate, SUM(SR.SuccSetupRate) AS TotalSuccSetupRate FROM PppoxPortConfig AS PC, PppoePortResults AS PR, Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults AS SR, Port AS Port WHERE PC.Handle == PR.ParentHnd AND PC.EmulationType == 'CLIENT' AND SR.Location = Port.Location AND Port.Handle = PC.ParentHnd

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_SystemSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationState, TotalExpectedSessions INTEGER, TotalSuccessConnectCount INTEGER,  TotalFailedConnectCount INTEGER, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, TotalFailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, TotalConfigConnectRate REAL, TotalSuccSetupRate REAL)

SELECT IterInfo.Iteration AS Iteration, IterInfo.IterationState AS IterationState, TotalExpectedSessions, TotalSuccessConnectCount,  TotalFailedConnectCount, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount, TotalFailedDisconnectCount, TotalConfigConnectRate, TotalSuccSetupRate FROM Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults, Pppoe_IterationInfo AS IterInfo

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_PortSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationState, Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, DisconnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, FailedDisconnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount)

SELECT IterInfo.Iteration AS Iteration, IterInfo.IterationState AS IterationState, Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, DisconnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, FailedDisconnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount FROM Pppoe_PortSummaryResults, Pppoe_IterationInfo AS IterInfo
SELECT EnablePercentTolerance, PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_ThresholdTable

SELECT IterInfo.Iteration AS 'Iteration', IterInfo.IterationState AS 'Test Phase', TotalExpectedSessions AS 'Total Expected Session Count', TotalSuccessConnectCount AS 'Total Success Connect Count', TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount AS 'Total Success Disconnect Count', TotalFailedConnectCount AS 'Total Failed Connect Count', TotalFailedDisconnectCount AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count', TotalConfigConnectRate AS 'Total Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)', TotalSuccSetupRate AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)', (SELECT PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_ThresholdTable) AS 'Rate Tolerance (%)' FROM Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults, Pppoe_IterationInfo AS IterInfo

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedPortsSessions (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, EnablePercentTolerance, PercentTolerance)

SELECT Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount FROM Pppoe_PortSummaryResults WHERE ConnectedSuccessCount != ExpectedSessions OR FailedConnectCount > 0

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedIterationsSessions (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationState, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate)

SELECT IterInfo.Iteration AS Iteration,IterInfo.IterationState AS IterationState, SUM(ExpectedSessions) AS ExpectedSessions, SUM(ConnectedSuccessCount) AS ConnectedSuccessCount, SUM(FailedConnectCount) AS FailedConnectCount, SUM(ConfigConnectRate) AS ConfigConnectRate, SUM(SuccSetupRate) AS SuccSetupRate FROM Pppoe_FailedPortsSessions, Pppoe_IterationInfo AS IterInfo
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS val_Iteration_PPPoE_Session_Results

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: All PPPoE sessions connected successfully without failures.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE name='val_Iteration_PPPoE_Session_Results')) > 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Not all PPPoE sessions connected successfully or failures were detected.

sql_statement.static: SELECT Iteration, IterationState AS 'Test Phase', ExpectedSessions AS 'Expected Session Count', ConnectedSuccessCount AS 'Successful Connect Count', FailedConnectCount AS 'Failed Connect Count' FROM Pppoe_FailedIterationsSessions WHERE Iteration = (SELECT Iteration FROM PppoeSummary_IterationInfo)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedPortsRate (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, EnablePercentTolerance, PercentTolerance)

SELECT Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, Thr.EnablePercentTolerance AS EnablePercentTolerance, Thr.PercentTolerance AS PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_PortSummaryResults, Pppoe_ThresholdTable AS Thr WHERE (SuccSetupRate < (ConfigConnectRate - (Thr.PercentTolerance * 0.01 * ConfigConnectRate))) OR (SuccSetupRate > (ConfigConnectRate + (Thr.PercentTolerance * 0.01 * ConfigConnectRate)))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedIterationsRate (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationState, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IteratorEndState (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, EnableStabilityBackoff, SearchMinVal, SearchMaxVal, StabilityRepeatCount, StabilityBackoffStep, StabilitySuccessPercent, IsConverged, ConvergedVal, FoundStableValue, StableValue)

SELECT EnableStabilityBackoff, MinVal AS SearchMinVal, MaxVal AS SearchMaxVal, RepeatCount AS StabilityRepeatCount, StepVal AS StabilityBackoffStep, SuccessPercent AS StabilitySuccessPercent, IsConverged, ConvergedVal, FoundStableValue, StableValue FROM spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand WHERE (SELECT Iter.Handle FROM Tag AS Tag, RelationTable AS RT, spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand AS Iter WHERE Tag.Name='spirent.methodology.benchmarkstabilityiteratorcommand.11111' AND RT.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle AND RT.SourceHnd=Iter.Handle AND RT.Type='UserTag')
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_ScaleResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, IsConverged, ConvergedVal)
SELECT IsConverged, ConvergedVal FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_StabilityResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, EnableStabilityBackoff, FoundStableValue, StableValue)
SELECT EnableStabilityBackoff, FoundStableValue, StableValue FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_StabilityScaleValueResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, StabilityScaleValueResult)

SELECT (CASE WHEN ES.EnableStabilityBackoff=1 THEN (CASE WHEN Stability.FoundStableValue=1 THEN Stability.StableValue ELSE 0 END) ELSE (CASE WHEN Scale.IsConverged=1 THEN Scale.ConvergedVal ELSE 0 END) END) AS StabilityScaleValueResult FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState AS ES, Pppoe_StabilityResult AS Stability, Pppoe_ScaleResult AS Scale

report.explanation: Verifies that the search phase of the session scale benchmarking converged on a final value.

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: A session scale value that included no session failures was not found.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN Scal.IsConverged=0 THEN 0 WHEN Stab.EnableStabilityBackoff=1 AND Stab.FoundStableValue=0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END FROM Pppoe_ScaleResult AS Scal, Pppoe_StabilityResult AS Stab

sql_statement.static: SELECT (CASE WHEN Scal.IsConverged=0 THEN 'N/A' ELSE Scal.ConvergedVal END) AS 'Session Scale', (CASE WHEN Stab.EnableStabilityBackoff=0 THEN 'Stability Backoff Disabled' ELSE Stab.StableValue END) AS 'Stable Session Count' FROM Pppoe_StabilityResult AS Stab, Pppoe_ScaleResult AS Scal

SELECT Iteration AS 'Iteration', (case when TotalExpectedSessions != TotalSuccessConnectCount or TotalFailedConnectCount > 0 then 'FAIL' else 'PASS' end) as 'Verdict', (CASE WHEN IterationState='SEARCH' THEN 'Binary Search' ELSE 'Stability' END) AS 'Test Phase', TotalExpectedSessions AS 'Total Expected Session Count', TotalSuccessConnectCount AS 'Total Successful Connection Count', TotalFailedConnectCount AS 'Total Failed Connection Count', TotalFailedDisconnectCount AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count', TotalConfigConnectRate AS 'Total Config Rate (sessions/s)', TotalSuccSetupRate AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (session/s)' FROM Pppoe_SystemSummaryResults
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PPPoEScaleSessionCount (ConvergedSessionCount INTEGER, StableSessionCount INTEGER, ExpectedSessionCount INTEGER)
SELECT (CASE WHEN (select IsConverged from Pppoe_ScaleResult) = 0 THEN 'Did not converge' ELSE (select ConvergedVal from Pppoe_ScaleResult) END) AS 'ConvergedSessionCount',

(select case when EnableStabilityBackoff = 0 then 'Stability test disabled' when EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 and FoundStableValue = 0 then 'No stable session rate found'  when EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 and FoundStableValue > 0 then StableValue end from Pppoe_StabilityResult) AS StableSessionCount,
(select ExpectedSessionCount from Pppoe_SessionCountThresholdTable) AS ExpectedSessionCount

report.explanation: Converged session count meets the session count threshold.

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Converged session count and stable session count meet the session count threshold.
report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Converged session count or Stable session count is less than the session count threshold.

sql_for_verdict.static: select case when (EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 and FoundStableValue = 0) or (IsConverged = 0) or (IsConverged = 1 and cast(ConvergedVal as INTEGER) < (select ExpectedSessionCount from Pppoe_SessionCountThresholdTable)) or (FoundStableValue=1 AND cast(StableValue as INTEGER)< (select ExpectedSessionCount from Pppoe_SessionCountThresholdTable)) then 0 else 1 end from Pppoe_ScaleResult, Pppoe_StabilityResult
